data.description: Discover your dream condo in the heart of the coveted Tanglewood neighborhood, where modern luxury meets lush natural surroundings. This renovated 3-bed, 2-bath condo is a sanctuary of comfort and elegance, flooded with natural light through its large windows. The spacious bedrooms offer both style and functionality, while the two contemporary bathrooms provide the ultimate in relaxation and convenience. The standout feature of this condo is the expansive wrap-around private balcony, granting you panoramic views of the lush bayou. It's the perfect spot to start your day with a cup of coffee or to host friends with the bayou as your backdrop. You'll enjoy the added convenience of a private parking space conveniently located near your unit. Plus, rest easy knowing that your security is ensured by the guard-gated entrance. Nestled in the prestigious Tanglewood neighborhood, this condo offers not only modern luxury but also a unique connection to nature that defines this charming area.
